                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-126-off752 t18281023-126-crimeloc754"></join>. On the 30th of September the watch-house-keeper came and asked if I had lost a bedstead - I said No, but found I had.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281023-126-person730">
                  THOMAS 
                  WALKER
               <interp inst="t18281023-126-person730" type="surname" value="WALKER"></interp>
