            . I am the watch-house-keeper. On the 30th of September, about eleven o'clock. I saw the prisoner looking at the bedstead; he then took it up, and went away with it - I went and spoke to Mrs. Pearson, who said he had stolen it; I went and took him with it.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded poverty.</p>
